Always follow SYSTEM_PROMPT.md and ARCHITECTURE.md.
Do not introduce cloud services.
Do not introduce autonomous behavior.
Do not bypass human-in-the-loop constraints.
Prefer clarity over cleverness.
Explain architectural changes before coding.
Always respect the project's cost and tooling constraints.

Never suggest:
- Paid APIs
- Cloud services
- Token-based AI usage
- SaaS monitoring tools

Refer to docs/constraints.md before proposing tools or architectures.
